all under level 60 with no tanks or healers. We mezzed him, drained his mana for about 5 min just to make sure we had it all, and then when he can't nuke, he is a major wuss. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://graffes.netfirms.com/smiley/solro.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> Pyroshane Flamethrower <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://graffes.netfirms.com/smiley/solro.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Level 56 (for 4 months already) Wizard</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">GNOME POWER!</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yilar44>Yilar44</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 415<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/4/03 3:25:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26377.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mob Mana</span><hr size=1> first off: Phinny's Melee dmg &gt;&gt;&gt; Phinny's Nuke dmg.<br>
<br>
Also id like to add that if you dont agro the mobs they have unlimited mana, so if your killing a mob somewhere and healer mob passes by, the healer mob can heal the other mob for a very long time.  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=43436" target="top">Yilar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
