Mith Marr</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=istari@graffeswizardcompilation>Istari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 200<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/4/03 9:48:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26377.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hm</span><hr size=1> it's just that unaggro'd mobs regen at a ridiculous rate. I notice a health point regen of 20%/tick, and I would think that the huge regen rate applies to mana.<br>
<br>
in this game of massively scaled up mob melee damage and large player resists, not even the mob's chain nuked spells compare with its melee damage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sellasteel>Sella Steel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/4/03 12:02:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26377.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: hm</span><hr size=1> When I used to solo the forager cycle (in TT) with my bard I would frequently charm the named casters onto garbage mobs just to waste their mana.  It definitely makes a differnce when they're not stopping to cast ice comet on you every once in a while. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177145" target="top">Sella</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Virtuoso</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pinepath>Pinepath</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/6/03 9:47:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26377.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Mob mana</span><hr size=1> Mobs do have a finite mana pool, and it actually seems pretty small for most.  Back when black acrylia weapons came out, I did some farming of the 4arm guys in Maiden's Eye, and the easiest way for me to kill them, was to hang around in their cast range and let them nuke me till they were OOM, before killing them.  <br>
<br>
Otherwise, 10k CHs would make killing them an ordeal.<br>
<br>
At some point though, they apparently increased the manaregen rate of high level mobs,  55-56+, somewhere around there.  It was after a patch, that I noticed the 4arms, drained completely oom, regenned enough each tick to cast a heal (80 pt one).  Completely OOM and rooted/snared, they would still chain cast their 80pt heal with no breaks, I let one do it for several minutes once.  They didn't do that before the patch, and lower level ones, like the robe clerics in the same zone, didn't change.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xajkil@graffeswizardcompilation>Xajkil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/7/03 5:49:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26377.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mob mana</span><hr size=1> Another easy wasy to tell is to meele the orc oracles in oasis orc highway.  As long as you don't do too much damage too fast, they'll get off 2-3 heals to themselves.  After those 2-3 heals, they'll stop trying to cast and eventually get taken down to flee hps.<br>
<br>
I also fought the same orcs 3 years ago and they acted the same.  So my guess is that they've always had finite mana, but back in the day uber MOBs either had insane mana and/or insane mana regen.  That would basically mean they have unlimited mana and is what some other people remember. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=26377.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=26377.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26377.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.graffe.com/images/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=26377.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=26377.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26377.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26377.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellp